# Plot PCoA Weighted Unifrac ajustado com variável contínua COLESTEROL
ggplot(merge(wunifrac.pcoa$points, subset(metadados_dieta, !is.na(residual_cobre_mg)), by.x = "row.names", by.y = "IdVoluntario")) + 
  geom_point(aes(x = V1, y = V2, color = residual_cobre_mg), size = 2) + 
  scale_color_gradient(low = "blue", high = "red", name = "residual_cobre_mg") +
  labs(title = "Weighted Unifrac", x = "V1", y = "V2") +
  theme_minimal()
